*Ljubomoran* je on na nju. (He is jealous of her.)
Njegovo ponašanje je zato što je *ljubomoran*. (His behavior is because he is jealous.)
Nisam *ljubomoran*, samo me brine. (I'm not jealous, I'm just worried.)
On se oseća *ljubomorno* kada je vidi sa drugim momcima. (He feels jealous when he sees her with other guys.)
Uvek sam bio *ljubomoran* prema njemu. (I have always been jealous of him.)